```plantuml
@startuml victorshinya_serverless-chatbot
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "IBM Cloud Functions" as CloudFunctions #aliceblue {
  rectangle "assistant.js\nFunction" as AssistantFunction #lightsteelblue
  rectangle "mongodb.js\nFunction" as MongoDBFunction #lightyellow
}

rectangle "Watson Assistant" as WatsonAssistant #palegreen

rectangle "MongoDB" as MongoDB #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> AssistantFunction : Send message

' Assistant function interactions
AssistantFunction --> WatsonAssistant : Submit user input\nReceive response

' MongoDB function interactions
AssistantFunction --> MongoDBFunction : Send conversation data
MongoDBFunction --> MongoDB : Store conversation data

@enduml
```